data.title: Fergusons of Derry (Londonderry)
data.text:
36511 Saml 22 Lderry P Farmer 7 Apr 70 Resigned 12.5.70 to go home 37614 Robt Jno 25 Lderry Pres Laborer 6 Apr 71 Antrim Resigned 27 Dec 1877 to better his position Ferguson, owise Rainey, Mary
